verbose_text: For example, in antipsychotic naive FEP, levels of the anti-inflammatory cytokine IL-10 inversely correlate with PANSS negative scores [XREF_BIBR], indicating this anti-inflammatory marker is associated with less severe symptoms, however PANSS positive scores in FEP have been observed to inversely correlate with pro inflammatory IL-6 [XREF_BIBR].
evidence: levels of the anti-inflammatory cytokine IL-10
